headline: Brown & Brown : acquires Premier Commercial
summary: London, UK: Brown & Brown Ltd, part of Brown & Brown Inc. , has acquired 100% of the share capital of Premier Commercial Ltd , an Edinburgh based MGA and Lloyd's Coverholder. ...
